column2: SELECT AlbumID, SUM (UnitPrice) AS totalPrice, COUNT (AlbumID) AS numTracks FROM chinook.Track GROUP BY AlbumID) SELECT TOP # album.Title AS #, artist.Name AS #, f.totalPrice AS #, f.numTracks AS # FROM f JOIN chinook.Album album ON album.AlbumID = f.AlbumID JOIN chinook.Artist artist ON artist.ArtistID = album.ArtistID ORDER BY totalPrice DESC
